{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they came to the destination, all these people-- and when I say, 'the most prominent,' I mean lawyers and doctors and professors and mathematicians and scientists, you name it-- 150 of them, and they-- they had to get off the trucks and under the-- under the Gestapo guard and their dogs, of course, that they assign.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they said-- [SPEAKING GERMAN], that dog ripped you apart to shreds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing left of you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so this happened to a pregnant woman, and I'll tell you when and why.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had to-- get-- they were ordered to get undressed and fold their clothes neatly and empty out their pockets, whatever there is of value, to empty it out and put it in a box which was provided by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and they put all these things in, including gold teeth, whatever was removed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they were given a-- they were all stark naked, they were taken to shovels, and they are to dig a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When this was done, they were forced to face the ditch, and they were shot in the back into the ditches.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One man managed to climb out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they fell one on top of another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even if the ditch was six feet tall, whatever, he could still manage to climb up and come out of the-- and come out of the grave.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My cousin's father was among them but he was not shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were women also standing naked, but somehow, they did not kill the women at that point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were stand-- there were women standing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He hid among the women, and this is how he went away-- went away with them, my uncle Joseph, the one who is with my father in the picture.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
